1.To Remove git from a project
	rm -rf .git

2. Check the repo origin

   git remote -v
   
3. To a git to an existion solution ( after creating the repo online)
now you can init your repository with


git init
git add .
git commit -m "first commit"
git branch -M main
git remote add origin https://github.com/Akomspatrick/NewTemplateManager.git
git push -u origin main

4. To add Git ignore to a dotnet solution
 dotnet new gitignore